e international Life-Link conference in Sweden 6-10 August 2007. The organisation of the conference and excursions was wonderfully arranged.\r\nThe conference will be considered as part of a Russia â€“ Sweden Upgrade Cultural programme running 2006.\r\n\r\nA follow up discussion took place 11 Oct at Moscow school 1414 ecological annex Cheveriyovo.','conferences/2006_ru_oct',NULL,643,'no');
